National Oilwell Varco Reports First Quarter 2017 Results

























HOUSTON--(BUSINESS WIRE)--Apr. 26, 2017-- National Oilwell Varco, Inc. (NYSE: NOV) today reported a first quarter 2017 net loss of $122 million, or $0.32 per share. Excluding other items, net loss for the quarter was $63 million, or $0.17 per share. Other items totaled $37 million, pretax, and primarily consisted of charges related to severance and facility closures.
