 in Houston, TX.    expand             Key People National Oilwell Varco Inc.   Board of Directors    Name/Title Current Board Membership          Clay C. Williams, 52  Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer   National Oilwell Varco, Inc., Benchmark Electronics, Inc., Sam Houston Area Council      James T. Hackett, 63  Independent Non-Executive Director   National Oilwell Varco, Inc.      Greg L. Armstrong, 57  Lead Independent Non-Executive Director   National Oilwell Varco, Inc.      William R. Thomas, 63  Independent Non-Employee Director   National Oilwell Varco, Inc.      Marcela E. Donadio, 61  Independent Non-Employee Director   National Oilwell Varco, Inc.      David D. Harrison, 67  Independent Non-Employee Director   National Oilwell Varco, Inc.      Benjamin Allen Guill, 65  Independent Non-Employee Director   National Oilwell Varco, Inc.      Eric L. Mattson, 63  Independent Non-Employee Director   National Oilwell Varco, Inc.       expand    All Executives     Clay C. Williams Chairman, President & Chief Executive Officer     Jose A. Bayardo Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President     Alex Philips Chief Information Security Officer     Hege Kverneland Chief Technology Officer & Vice President     Bonnie Houston SVP-Human Resources & Administration     Bill Crabbe Chief Health, Safety & Environment Officer     Kirk Shelton President-Completion & Production Solutions     Joseph W. Rovig President-Rig Systems & Rig Aftermarket     Brigitte Hunt Vice President     David Reid Chief Marketing Officer     Scott K. Duff Chief Accounting Officer, VP & Controller     Loren Singletary Vice President-Investor & Industry Relations     Craig L. Weinstock Secretary, Senior Vice President & General Counsel     James T. Hackett Independent Non-Executive Director     Greg L. Armstrong Lead Independent Non-Executive Director     William R. Thomas Independent Non-Employee Director     Marcela E. Donadio Independent Non-Employee Director     David D. Harrison